Package: xhub
Version: 0.0.11-4
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: xhelix authors <maintainers@xhelix.dev>
Depends: libc6
Description: xhelix fleet baseline hub
 xhub receives per-binary behavioural feature aggregates from xhelix
 agents across a fleet and serves cross-fleet "rare endpoint" lists
 back to agents for elevated-confidence detection.
 .
 Single static binary, runs under systemd. Pair with one or more
 xhelix agents that have baseline.hub.url pointed at this server.
Homepage: https://github.com/xhelix/xhelix
